OL,3,CCybersecurity software bug affects
OL,4,Cbroadcasters
OL,6,GSky News, Sky Sports and CBBC were
OL,7,Gamong the TV channels impacted by a
OL,8,Gbug in a new release of software
OL,9,Grolled out globally by cybersecurity
OL,10,Gcompany CrowdStrike.
OL,12,FProblems were apparent on Sky News
OL,13,Fshortly before 6am, when an apology
OL,14,Fgraphic appeared. A short time later,
OL,15,Fthe channel switched to a back-up
OL,16,Fschedule of pre-recorded programming.
