OL,4,Cbroadcasters
OL,6,FLive output resumed at 8.49am. But the
OL,7,Fchannel had to make do with no
OL,8,Fautocue, graphics or packages for a
OL,9,Fnumber of hours, with presenters Anna
OL,10,FJones and Gareth Barlow reading off
OL,11,Fpaper scripts.
OL,13,FNormal service was more or less
OL,14,Fresumed shortly after lunchtime.
OL,16,FSky Sports News displayed an apology
OL,17,Fgraphic for some time in the morning,
OL,18,Fbefore simulcasting Sky Sports Golf.
OL,19,FNormal service was gradually restored
OL,20,Fduring the afternoon.
