OL,3,CCybersecurity software bug affects
OL,4,Cbroadcasters
OL,6,FCBBC's schedule fell off air at
OL,7,F7.55am, after a live edition of
OL,8,FNewsround. It's understood that
OL,9,Fexiting the live event caused the
OL,10,Fplayout system to crash.
OL,12,FBBC One, BBC Two and CBeebies playout
OL,13,Fwould've been similarly affected.
OL,15,FHowever, CBeebies had no live events
OL,16,Fin its schedule. BBC Two didn't have
OL,17,Fto exit a live event until lunchtime.
OL,18,FA fix was implemented prior to that.
