OL,3,CCybersecurity software bug affects
OL,4,Cbroadcasters
OL,6,FBBC One was due to exit a live event
OL,7,F(Morning Live) at 10.45am. Rather than
OL,8,Fbeing put to air by BBC One playout,
OL,9,FMorning Live was initially passed
OL,10,Fthrough the BBC Breakfast gallery.
OL,12,FAs we understand it, a fix was applied
OL,13,Fto BBC One playout just prior to
OL,14,F10.45am, and the channel's planned
OL,15,Fschedule was played out normally.
OL,17,FCrowdStrike CEO George Kurtz said:
OL,18,F"CrowdStrike is actively working with
OL,19,Fcustomers impacted by a defect found
OL,20,Fin a single content update for Windows
OL,21,Fhosts. Mac and Linux hosts are not
OL,22,Fimpacted.
